kiss]]<ref name=\"Hough\">{{Cite web|url=http://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/news/business/s/116/116097_hough_is_new_high_sheriff.html|title=Hough is new High Sheriff |date=5 October 2004|publisher=manchestereveningnews.co.uk|accessdate=5 May 2008|author=Moore, Sheryl}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2004 || [[Robert Eric Hough]]<ref name=\"TopCop\"/><ref name=\"Hough\"/>\n|-\n| 2005 || Chief Constable Sir [[David Wilmot (police officer)|David Wilmot]]<ref name=\"TopCop\">{{cite web|url=http://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/news/s/153/153494_from_top_cop_to_high_sheriff.html|title=From top cop to High Sheriff|publisher=manchestereveningnews.co.uk|date=5 April 2005|author=Britton, Paul|accessdate=5 May 2008}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2006 || [[Alexandra Burslem]]<ref>{{London Gazette|issue=57921|page=3375|date=9 March 2006}}</ref>\n|-\n|-\n| 2007 || [[Michael Oglesby]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.piccadillymanchester.com/index.asp?Sessionx=IpqiNwF6IwxqNwB6IaqiNwA|title=Introducing the High Sheriff of Greater Manchester|publisher=piccadillymanchester.com|date=8 May 2007|accessdate=5 May 2008|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071212045240/http://www.piccadillymanchester.com/index.asp?Sessionx=IpqiNwF6IwxqNwB6IaqiNwA|archive-date=12 December 2007|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2008 || [[Edith Conn]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/news/s/1045649_hats_off_to_the_sheriff_|title=Hats off to the sheriff |date=17 April 2008|publisher=manchestereveningnews.co.uk|accessdate=5 May 2008|author=McCathie, Charlie}} {{Dead link|date=October 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2009 || Christian Wewer DL<ref>{{London Gazette|issue=59011|page=4924|date=19 March 2009}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2010 || Anil Ruia OBE JP DL of Didsbury<ref name=\"www.highsheriffs.com Index\">{{cite web |url= http://www.highsheriffs.com/Greater%20Manchester/Index.htm|title = Greater Manchester 2012/2013| publisher=The High sheriff's Association of England and Wales|accessdate = 4 April 2012}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2011 |