lisher=Sacred Heart Church|accessdate=April 19, 2020|url=https://www.shsalinas.org/about-sh/history/}}</ref>\n|-\n|St. Angela Merici\n|\n|362 Lighthouse Ave, [[Pacific Grove, California|Pacific Grove]]\n|Founded in 1928 with first church completed in 1929; current church built 1956<ref>{{cite web|title=Parish History|publisher=St. Angela Merici|accessdate=April 19, 2020|url=https://stangelamericipacificgrove.org/parish-history}}</ref>\n|-\n|St. Francis Xavier\n|\n|1475 La Salle Ave, [[Seaside, California|Seaside]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Home page|publisher=St. Francis Xavier Catholic Church|accessdate=April 19, 2020|url=http://www.stfxavier.org/}}</ref>\n|-\n|St. John the Baptist\n|\n|504 N 3rd St, [[King City, California|King City]]\n|\n|-\n|St. Joseph's \n|\n|1 Railroad Ave, [[Spreckels, California|Spreckels]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=A Brief History of Saint Joseph\u2019s Catholic Church|publisher=Saint Joseph's Catholic Parish|accessdate=April 19, 2020|url=https://stjchurch.org/parish-history}}</ref>\n|-\n|St. Jude\n|\n|303 Hillcrest Ave, [[Marina, California|Marina]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=St. Jude Catholic Parish|accessdate=April 19, 2020|url=https://stjudemarina.org/}}</ref>\n|-\n|St. Mary of the Nativity\n|\n|424 Towt St, Salinas\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Home page|publisher=St Mary of the Nativity Catholic Church|accessdate=April 19, 2020|url=http://www.stmarysalinas.org/}}</ref>\n|-\n|St. Theodore's\n|\n|125 S Center St, [[Gonzales, California|Gonzales]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=St Theodore Catholic Church|publisher=Facebook|accessdate=April 19, 2020|url=https://www.facebook.com/pages/category/Religious-Organization/St-Theodore-Catholic-Church-Gonzales-California-770312033351251/}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===San Benito County===\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:75%\"\n! style=\"background:darkviolet; color:yellow;\" width=\"25%\" |'''Name'''\n! style=\"background:darkviolet; color:yellow;\" width=\"10%\" |'''Image'''\n! style=\"background:darkviolet; color