alifornia|Pismo Beach]]\n|<ref>https://www.stpaulspismobeach.com/</ref>\n|-\n|St. Rose of Lima\n|\n|820 Creston Rd, [[Paso Robles, California|Paso Robles]]\n|<ref>http://www.saintrosechurch.org/word/</ref>\n|-\n|St. Timothy\n|\n|962 Piney Way, [[Morro Bay, California|Morro Bay]]\n|<ref>https://www.sttimothymorrobay.org/</ref>\n|-\n|St. William's\n|\n|6410 Santa Lucia Rd, [[Atascadero, California|Atascadero]]\n|<ref>https://www.stwilliams.org/</ref>\n|-\n|Santa Margarita de Cortona\n|\n|22515 H St, [[Santa Margarita, California|Santa Margarita]]\n|\n|-\n|Santa Rosa\n|\n|1174 Main St, [[Cambria, California|Cambria]]\n|<ref>https://www.santarosaparish.org/</ref>\n|}\n\n===Santa Cruz County===\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:75%\"\n! style=\"background:darkviolet; color:yellow;\" width=\"25%\" |'''Name'''\n! style=\"background:darkviolet; color:yellow;\" width=\"10%\" |'''Image'''\n! style=\"background:darkviolet; color:yellow;\" width=\"25%\" |'''Location'''\n! style=\"background:darkviolet; color:yellow;\" width=\"15\" |'''Description/Notes'''\n|-\n|Christ Child\n|\n|23230 Summit Rd, [[Los Gatos, California|Los Gatos]]\n|<ref>https://christchild.org/</ref>\n|-\n|[[Mission Santa Cruz|Holy Cross Church]]\n|[[File:MissionSantaCruzCalifornia.jpg|100px]]\n|210 High St, [[Santa Cruz, California|Santa Cruz]]\n|Former [[Mission Santa Cruz]]<ref>https://holycrosssantacruz.com/</ref>\n|-\n|Holy Eucharist\n|\n|527 Corralitos Rd, [[Corralitos, California|Corralitos]]\n|<ref>https://www.holyeucharistca.com/</ref>\n|-\n|Our Lady Star of the Sea\n|\n|515 Frederick St, Santa Cruz\n|<ref>http://www.ourladystar.org/</ref>\n|-\n|Resurrection\n|\n|7600 Soquel Dr, [[Aptos, California|Aptos]]\n|<ref>https://resurrection-aptos.org/</ref>\n|-\n|St. John's\n|\n|120 Russell Ave, [[Felton, California|Felton]]\n|<ref>http://www.stjohnsfelton.org/</ref>\n|-\n|St. Joseph's \n|\n|435 Monterey Ave, [[Capitola, California|Capitola]]\n|<ref>https://saint-josephs.church/</ref>\n|-\n|St. Michael's\n|\n|13005 Pine St, [[Boulder Creek, California|Boulder Creek]]\n|<ref>http://www.st-michaelschurch.org/</ref>\n|-\n|San Agustin\n|\n|257 Glenwood Drive, [[Scotts Valley, California|Scotts Valley]]\n|\n|-\n|Shrine of St. Joseph\n|\n|544 W Cliff Dr, Santa Cruz\n|<ref>https://shrinestjoseph.com/</ref>\n|}\n\n==High schools==\n* [[Mission College Preparatory High School]], San Luis Obispo\n* [[Old Mission Elementary School]], San Luis Obispo\n* [[Notre Dame High School (Salinas, California)|Notre Dame High School]], Salinas\n* [[Palma High School]], Salinas\n* [[Saint Francis Central Coast Catholic High School]], Watsonville\n* [[Santa Catalina School]], Monterey\n\n==See also==\n{{Portal|Catholicism}}\n* [[Catholic Church by country]]\n* [[Catholic Church hierarchy]]\n* [[List of the Catholic dioceses of the United States]]\n\n==Sources==\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20051226141134/http://www.dioceseofmonterey.org/history.htm ''History'' article from the Diocese's website]\n*[http://www.dcsmonterey.org/index.shtml Catholic Schools of the Monterey Diocese]\n*[http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dmont.html ''Catholic-Hierarchy.Org'' datasheet]\n\n{{commons category}}\n\n== References ==\n<references />\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.dioceseofmonterey.org/ Roman Catholic Diocese of Monterey Official Site]\n*[http://www.sancarloscathedral.org/ Cathedral of San Carlos Borromeo website]\n\n{{Roman Catholic Diocese of Monterey in California}}\n{{Roman Catholic Ecclesiastical Province of Los Angeles}}\n{{coord|36.6000|N|121.9000|W|source:wikidata-and-enwiki-cat-tree_region:US|display=title}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Roman Catholic Diocese of Monterey in California| ]]\n[[Category:Monterey County, California]]\n[[Category:San Benito County, California]]\n[[Category:San Luis Obispo County, California]]\n[[Category:Santa Cruz County, California]]\n[[Category:The Californias]]\n[[Category:Religious organizations established in 1840|Monterey in 